{"id":"572","name":"ridewell-this-saturday-with-bloodwater","title":"Ride:Well This Saturday with Blood:Water","author":"Morgan Levy","date":"2008-07-08T07:45:00-05:00","tags":["3rd &amp; lindsley","blood:water mission","july 12","matthew perryman jones","ride well tour","rocketown","sixpence none the richer"],"categories":["Culture &amp; Arts","Music City"],"contentEncoded":"<div id=\"greet_block\"><noscript><div class=\"greet_block wpgb_cornered\"><div class=\"greet_text\"><div class=\"greet_image\"><a href=\"http://nashvillest.com/feed/rss/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"http://nashvillest.com/wp-content/plugins/wp-greet-box/images/rss_icon.png\" alt=\"WP Greet Box icon\"></a></div>Hello there! If you&apos;re new to Nashvillest, you might want to <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/nashvillest\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>subscribe to our RSS feed</strong></a> to make sure you don&apos;t miss anything! We&apos;re also on <a href=\"https://twitter.com/#!/nashvillest\" target=\"blank\"><strong>Twitter</strong></a> if you&apos;d like to join us there!<div style=\"clear:both\"></div><div class=\"greet_block_powered_by\">Powered by <a href=\"http://omninoggin.com/projects/wordpress-plugins/wp-greet-box-wordpress-plugin/\" title=\"WP Greet Box WordPress Plugin\" style=\"text-decoration:none;\">WP Greet Box</a> <a href=\"http://omninoggin.com/\" title=\"WordPress Plugin\" style=\"text-decoration:none;\">WordPress Plugin</a></div><div style=\"clear:both\"></div></div></div></noscript></div><p><a href=\"http://nashvillest.com/wp-content/uploads/2008/07/nashvilleposter.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-573\" title=\"nashvilleposter\" src=\"http://nashvillest.com/wp-content/uploads/2008/07/nashvilleposter.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"755\"></a></p><p>We&#x2019;ve talked about Blood:Water Mission and their Ride:Well tour before, but now they&#x2019;re almost here. Literally. The team of riders that are biking across the United States will arrive here this weekend for the local chapter of the Ride:Well tour on Saturday. The Nashville ride is 25 miles, but there will be a 12 mile version for those out-of-shape bikers among us, and will start downtown at Rocketown (6th &amp; Shirley) at 9am.</p><p>Registration for Saturday&#x2019;s ride starts at a $50 donation, but different levels of registration are available with different incentives. <a href=\"http://www.ridewelltour.com/CITYRIDES/NashvilleJuly12/tabid/1679/Default.aspx\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.ridewelltour.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">Register now online</a>, or on-site at 8am the day of the ride.</p><p>If you&#x2019;re lazy and bike-less like us, come out to support Blood:Water at their follow-up fundraising concert Sunday evening at <a href=\"http://3rdandlindsley.com/\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;3rdandlindsley.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">3rd &amp; Lindsley</a>. Sixpence None The Richer and Matthew Perryman Jones will be playing (don&#x2019;t forget to get Matthew Perryman Jones&#x2019; album on <a href=\"http://www.noisetrade.com\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.noisetrade.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">Noisetrade</a>) and all proceeds benefit Blood:Water Mission.</p><p>Related posts:<ol><li><a href=\"http://nashvillest.com/2008/05/29/nashvillest-spotlight-bloodwater-mission/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Permanent Link: Nashvillest Spotlight: Blood:Water Mission\">Nashvillest Spotlight: Blood:Water Mission</a></li><li><a href=\"http://nashvillest.com/2010/03/22/world-water-day-walk-for-water-downtown-with-bloodwater-mission/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Permanent Link: World Water Day: Walk For Water Downtown With Blood:Water Mission\">World Water Day: Walk For Water Downtown With Blood:Water Mission</a></li><li><a href=\"http://nashvillest.com/2009/05